#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:2 ../../../installing-vyper.rst:74
#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:132
msgid "Installing Vyper"
msgstr "安裝 Vyper"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:4
msgid ""
"Take a deep breath, follow the instructions, and please `create an issue "
"<https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/issues>`_ if you encounter any errors."
msgstr ""
"深吸一口氣，按照說明操作，如果遇到任何錯誤，請`建立一個 Issue <https://"
"github.com/vyperlang/vyper/issues>`_。"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:10
msgid ""
"The easiest way to experiment with the language is to use either `Try Vyper! "
"<https://try.vyperlang.org>`_ (maintained by the Vyper team) or the `Remix "
"online compiler <https://remix.ethereum.org>`_ (maintained by the Ethereum "
"Foundation). - To use Try Vyper, go to https://try.vyperlang.org and log in "
"(requires Github login). - To use remix, go to https://remix.ethereum.org "
"and activate the vyper-remix plugin in the Plugin manager."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:16
msgid "Standalone"
msgstr "獨立安裝"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:18
msgid ""
"The Vyper CLI can be installed with any ``pip`` compatible tool, for "
"example, ``pipx`` or ``uv tool``. If you do not have ``pipx`` or ``uv`` "
"installed, first, go to the respective tool's installation page:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:20
msgid "https://github.com/pypa/pipx?tab=readme-ov-file"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:21
msgid "https://github.com/astral-sh/uv?tab=readme-ov-file#uv"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:23
msgid "Then, the command to install Vyper would be"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:27
msgid "pipx install vyper"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:29
msgid "Or,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:33
msgid "uv tool install vyper"
msgstr "uv tool install vyper"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:37
msgid "Binaries"
msgstr "二進位檔"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:39
msgid ""
"Alternatively, prebuilt Vyper binaries for Windows, Mac and Linux are "
"available for download from the GitHub releases page: https://github.com/"
"vyperlang/vyper/releases."
msgstr ""
"或者，可以在 GitHub releases 頁面下載適用於 Windows、Mac 和 Linux 的預編譯 "
"Vyper 二進位檔：https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/releases。"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:43
msgid "PIP"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:46
msgid "Installing Python"
msgstr "安裝 Python"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:48
msgid ""
"Vyper can only be built using Python 3.10 and higher. If you need to know "
"how to install the correct version of python, follow the instructions from "
"the official `Python website <https://wiki.python.org/moin/BeginnersGuide/"
"Download>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:52
msgid "Creating a virtual environment"
msgstr "建立虛擬環境"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:54
msgid ""
"Because pip installations are not isolated by default, this method of "
"installation is meant for more experienced Python developers who are using "
"Vyper as a library, or want to use it within a Python project with other pip "
"dependencies."
msgstr ""
"由於 pip 安裝預設不是隔離的，此安裝方法適用於更有經驗的 Python 開發者，他們"
"將 Vyper 作為函式庫使用，或希望在其他具有 pip 相依性的 Python 專案中使用它。"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:59
msgid ""
"It is **strongly recommended** to install Vyper in **a virtual Python "
"environment**, so that new packages installed and dependencies built are "
"strictly contained in your Vyper project and will not alter or affect your "
"other development environment set-up. For easy virtualenv management, we "
"recommend either `pyenv <https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv>`_ or `Poetry "
"<https://github.com/python-poetry/poetry>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:69
msgid ""
"To find out more about virtual environments, check out: `virtualenv guide "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/venv.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"要了解更多關於虛擬環境的資訊，請參閱：`virtualenv 指南 <https://docs.python."
"org/3/library/venv.html>`_。"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:76
msgid ""
"Each tagged version of vyper is uploaded to `pypi <https://pypi.org/project/"
"vyper/>`_, and can be installed using ``pip``: ::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:79
msgid "pip install vyper"
msgstr "pip install vyper"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:81
msgid "To install a specific version use: ::"
msgstr "要安裝特定版本，請使用：\\ ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:84
msgid "pip install vyper==0.4.0"
msgstr "pip install vyper==0.4.0"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:86
msgid ""
"You can check if Vyper is installed completely or not by typing the "
"following in your terminal/cmd: ::"
msgstr ""
"您可以透過在終端機/命令提示字元中輸入以下內容來檢查 Vyper 是否已完全安裝： ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:89
msgid "vyper --version"
msgstr "vyper --version"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:93
msgid "Docker"
msgstr "Docker"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:95
msgid ""
"Vyper can be downloaded as docker image from `dockerhub <https://hub.docker."
"com/r/vyperlang/vyper/tags?page=1&ordering=last_updated>`_: ::"
msgstr ""
"Vyper 可以從 `dockerhub <https://hub.docker.com/r/vyperlang/vyper/tags?"
"page=1&ordering=last_updated>`_ 下載為 docker 映像檔： ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:98
msgid "docker pull vyperlang/vyper"
msgstr "docker pull vyperlang/vyper"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:100
msgid "To run the compiler use the ``docker run`` command: ::"
msgstr "要執行編譯器，請使用 ``docker run`` 命令： ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:103
msgid "docker run -v $(pwd):/code vyperlang/vyper /code/<contract_file.vy>"
msgstr "docker run -v $(pwd):/code vyperlang/vyper /code/<contract_file.vy>"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:105
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can log into the docker image and execute vyper on the "
"prompt. ::"
msgstr "或者，您可以登入 docker 映像檔並在提示符中執行 vyper。 ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:108
msgid ""
"docker run -v $(pwd):/code/ -it --entrypoint /bin/bash vyperlang/vyper\n"
"root@d35252d1fb1b:/code# vyper <contract_file.vy>"
msgstr ""
"docker run -v $(pwd):/code/ -it --entrypoint /bin/bash vyperlang/vyper\n"
"root@d35252d1fb1b:/code# vyper <contract_file.vy>"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:111
msgid "The normal parameters are also supported, for example: ::"
msgstr "也支援一般參數，例如： ::"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:114
msgid ""
"docker run -v $(pwd):/code vyperlang/vyper -f abi /code/<contract_file.vy>\n"
"[{'name': 'test1', 'outputs': [], 'inputs': [{'type': 'uint256', 'name': "
"'a'}, {'type': 'bytes', 'name': 'b'}], 'constant': False, 'payable': False, "
"'type': 'function', 'gas': 441}, {'name': 'test2', 'outputs': [], 'inputs': "
"[{'type': 'uint256', 'name': 'a'}], 'constant': False, 'payable': False, "
"'type': 'function', 'gas': 316}]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:119
msgid ""
"If you would like to know how to install Docker, please follow their "
"`documentation <https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果您想了解如何安裝 Docker，請遵循其 `文件 <https://docs.docker.com/get-"
"docker/>`_。"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:122
msgid "nix"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:124
msgid ""
"View the versions supported through nix at `nix package search <https://"
"search.nixos.org/packages?"
"channel=21.05&show=vyper&from=0&size=50&sort=relevance&query=vyper>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:128
msgid ""
"The derivation for Vyper is located at  `nixpkgs <https://github.com/NixOS/"
"nixpkgs/blob/master/pkgs/development/compilers/vyper/default.nix>`_"
msgstr ""
"Vyper 的 derivation 位於 `nixpkgs <https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/blob/"
"master/pkgs/development/compilers/vyper/default.nix>`_"

#: ../../../installing-vyper.rst:136
msgid "nix-env -iA nixpkgs.vyper"
msgstr "nix-env -iA nixpkgs.vyper"
